OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Feasing during Friday evening to leave
OL,7,Fa dry night. Clear spells initially,
OL,8,Fthough cloud tending to build as the
OL,9,Fnight progresses. A few fog patches
OL,10,Fpossible. Not too chilly, but
OL,11,Frelatively cool in rural areas.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FA few bright spells possible
OL,14,Fearly on, but cloud increasing through
OL,15,Fthe day. Largely dry before rain
OL,16,Farrives into the evening, heavy at
OL,17,Ftimes. Still warm and increasingly
OL,18,Fhumid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
