OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FWet on
OL,6,FSunday with rain breaking to showers,
OL,7,Fpossibly thundery. Further showers
OL,8,FMonday, then easing Tuesday with
OL,9,Fsunnier spells emerging, though
OL,10,Ffeeling less warm as temperatures drop
OL,11,Fcloser to average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
